        <name>k_object_init</name>
        <param>
          <type>const void *</type>
          <declname>obj</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Lookup a kernel object and init its metadata if it exists. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Calling this on an object will make it usable from userspace. Intended to be called as the last statement in kernel object init functions.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>obj</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Address of the kernel object</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>This is an internal API. Do not use unless you are extending functionality in the Zephyr tree. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
